    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 32-35.</p><p>Twinned Inspiration</p><p>Starting at 22nd level, your inspiration has become even stronger. When you use your Bardic Inspiration, you can inspire one additional creature within range. In addition, when you use your Legendary Inspiration, you can choose to expend an extra Legendary Point to target one additional creature.</p></div>",
